ss interfaces specifically designed for your vehicle's make and model. This avoids hacking or cutting factory wiring harnesses, maintaining your manufacturer's warranty safety standard guidelines."}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","button",null,{"className":"faq-question","children":["How accurate are the PostyBridges GPS trackers?",["$","svg",null,{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":"20","height":"20","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"2","strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","children":["$","polyline",null,{"points":"6 9 12 15 18 9"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer","children":["$","p",null,{"children":"Our trackers feature high-sensitivity GLONASS and GPS dual band chips, providing location reporting accurate within 2.5 meters. Location coordinates update every 10 seconds on your active mobile dashboard."}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","button",null,{"className":"faq-question","children":["Can the Push-to-Start button upgrade be installed on any car?",["$","svg",null,{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":"20","height":"20","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"2","strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","children":["$","polyline",null,{"points":"6 9 12 15 18 9"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer","children":["$","p",null,{"children":"Yes, we can upgrade almost any key-ignition vehicle manufactured after 2000 to a push-to-start smart entry system. Some high-end luxury models require specialized bypass modules, which our team configures in-house."}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","button",null,{"className":"faq-question","children":["Do the speed limit governors affect car acceleration?",["$","svg",null,{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":"20","height":"20","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strok